flowchart TD
    subgraph Inference Interfaces
      A["CLI: python main.py"]
      A2["HTTP API: uvicorn api:app"]
    end

    A -->|phrase| B["Direct translation\n(Ollama model)"]
    A -->|file| C["translate_file\n(direction aware)"]
    A -->|interactive + use-rag| D["RAG setup"]
    A -->|direction flag\nlat-en or en-lat| B
    A -->|direction flag\nlat-en or en-lat| C
    A -->|direction flag\nlat-en or en-lat| D

    A2 -->|POST /translate| B
    A2 -->|POST /translate-file| C
    A2 -->|GET /health| O["health check"]

    C -->|read .txt lines| E["Title/section detection\nLIBER, headers, numbered"]
    E --> F["LLM translate chunks\nper direction"]
    F --> G["Write input_translated.txt\nper direction"]

    D --> H["load_documents\n(parallel texts, PDFs)"]
    H --> I["Recursive splitter\nchunk_size=500, overlap=50"]
    I --> J["Embeddings: all-MiniLM-L6-v2"]
    J --> K["Chroma DB persist to latinragdb"]
    K --> L["Retriever k=4"]
    L --> M["RetrievalQA with Ollama\nper direction prompt"]
    M --> N["Interactive Q&A\ntranslate + explain + sources"]

    subgraph Training Pipeline
      S0["HF dataset\nparallel-catholic-bible-versions"]
      S1["scripts/pull_source_texts.py\nvulgate_latin.txt + vulgate_english.txt"]
      T1["Aligned corpus\n*_latin.txt + *_english.txt"]
      T2["scripts/build_sft_dataset.py\ntrain.jsonl + eval.jsonl"]
      T3["scripts/train_lora.py\nLoRA/QLoRA fine-tune"]
      T4["Adapter artifact\ntraining/checkpoints/.../adapter"]
      T5["scripts/merge_lora.py\nmerged HF model"]
      T6["Optional serving conversion\n(HF runtime or GGUF/Ollama path)"]
      S0 --> S1 --> T1 --> T2 --> T3 --> T4 --> T5 --> T6
    end

    subgraph Inputs
      X["data/*.txt or *.pdf"]
      Y["*_latin.txt + *_english.txt"]
    end
    X --> H
    Y --> H
    Y --> T1

    subgraph Outputs
      G
      N
      T4
      T5
    end
